Russia Considers Export Duty For Thermal Coal, Kommersant Says

-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 
2011-06-14T04:05:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/russia-considers-export-duty-for-thermal-coal-kommersant-says.html
Russia may impose export duties on
thermal coal as domestic power stations face possible shortages
because coal miners increased exports to  Japan  following the
nuclear disaster at Fukusima,  Kommersant  reported, citing
unidentified people close to the Energy Ministry.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
 ikhrennikov@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Amanda Jordan at 
 ajordan11@bloomberg.net  